postcontent: I wanted to post this in hopes of saving people from themselves, but one can lead a horse to water, but ......etc etc. First off, know your gun laws before you do anything. Example: it is legal for you to keep a loaded handgun in your car as long as you can see it from the window. If it's in the glove box or under the seat not in a locked case, it's a concealed handgun. OR, Omaha leos will try to get people who don't live in city limits to bring their handguns into the city USING THIS SITE. If you don't have it registered there, you just broke omaha ordinance and the man will do his job and will take your weapon. Good work gentlemen. Secondly, where do some of these people get their #s? The scalping is over guys, please post accordingly? Everyone that reads your post has internet,and can look at the msrp. The first post I saw today had a weapon over msrp and it was shot already? If we wanted to get screwed we'd do our wives.  Finally, use common sense. You DON'T know who is on the other side, and you can only know what YOU are going to do, not them. My ranting is over now, thank you for your time
